<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <h1 class='text-center'>Welcome to Codebreaker</h1>
      <p>Codebreaker is a logic game in which a code-breaker tries to break a secret code created by a code-maker. The code-maker, creates a secret code of four numbers between 1 and 6.</p> 
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 <%= 'col-md-6' if current_game && !current_game.completed? %>">
      <a href="/game/new" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">New game</a>
    </div>
    <% if current_game && !current_game.completed? %>
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
        <a href="/game" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Continue game</a>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
